brother-label-printer (1.4.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Version 1.4.0
  * Added template selector to Text Only tab with horizontal and rotated 90° CCW options
  * Renamed Template 5 to "Text Rotated 90° CCW" for clarity
  * Rotated text template prints on long side with single-line text scaled to fit tape height

