brother-label-printer (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Version 1.3.0
  * Added Template 6: Text Above QR layout (inverse of Template 2)
  * Added Templates gallery tab to showcase all available templates
  * Improved Template 2: Removed box icon watermark, increased QR size to 85% for better scannability
  * Improved Template 3: Added extra right padding to prevent text cutoff
  * Updated template descriptions for clarity
  * Templates now use example.com for mock QR codes in gallery

